sentences: He played in the progressive rock/jazz fusion band Magma in the 1970s and was known for his use of electric amplification and experimentation on different sounds on the electric violin.

In 1994, he moved to New York City for two years.
In 2000, Lockwood recorded a tribute album to Grappelli.
